Class CustomExtractor

  • java.lang.Object

    bftsmart.tom.util.Extractor

    public class CustomExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements bftsmart.tom.util.Extractor
    Implementation of the bft smart extractor in order to save all responses from all the replicas All extractor messages will be save with a long as a key. This long identifies a request, so that multiple and concurrent requests all have a different set of messages
